txt.en: The second level of Barad Guldur is guarded by the twin enemies of Fire and Shadow. They must both be defeated within ten seconds of one another to ensure that their powers are lost to the Enemy.
Challenge: Two with One Blow Completed
Defeat the twins of Fire and Shadow within ten seconds of one another
The twin fiends of Fire and Shadow are in Barad Guldur.\n\nYou must successfully engage and defeat the twin enemies of Fire and Shadow within Barad Guldur within ten seconds of one another.
